Invites all States that have not yet done so to consider signing, ratifying or acceding to the United Nations conventions and agreements on transport and transit facilitation, including the International Convention on the Harmonization of Frontier Controls of Goods
United Nations, Treaty Series, vol. 1409, No. 23583. and the Customs Convention on the International Transport of Goods under Cover of TIR Carnets (TIR Convention);
Ibid., vol. 1079, No. 16510.
